Manchester United will take on Barcelona in the Champions League quarterfinal — a repeat of the 2009 and 2011 finals. The clash is the pick of what promises to be an exciting round of match-ups. Ajax Amsterdam and Juventus, who produced the standout performances in the last 16, drew each other.
